<P>__{(hands it to her)}
<D>__{here you are.}
<C>__{violet}
<P>__{(bitterly)}
<D>__{character? if i had any character, i'd...}
<C>__{george}
<D>__{it takes a lot of character to leave your home town and start all over again. he pulls some money from his pocket, and offers it to her.}
